- `F006` 已统一到 `analysis_models.py`，并补了 `app.py` 显式 import，见 [phase1-plan.md:71](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L71), [phase1-plan.md:262](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L262)。
