FAIL。R1 标记为已解决的 `F002/F003/F007/F008` 仍未实质关闭；另外发现 2 条新的实现风险。`F001/F004/F005/F006` 本轮复核通过。

**Findings**

1. `F002`
Severity: HIGH  
Category: test-gap  
Type: defect_fix  
Before-behavior: plan 声称“Task 1-11 已补齐测试契约”，但实际上只有 Task 1/2/3/5/7/9 出现 `测试契约` 段。  
After-behavior: 所有行为变更 Task 都应包含完整 5 字段测试契约，并且边界条件至少 3 条。  
Evidence: Task 标题在 [phase1-plan.md:128](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L128), [phase1-plan.md:316](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L316), [phase1-plan.md:714](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L714), [phase1-plan.md:929](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L929), [phase1-plan.md:1157](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L1157), [phase1-plan.md:1315](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L1315), [phase1-plan.md:1467](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L1467), [phase1-plan.md:1784](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L1784), [phase1-plan.md:1905](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L1905), [phase1-plan.md:2179](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L2179), [phase1-plan.md:2384](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L2384), [phase1-plan.md:2492](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L2492)；但 `测试契约` 只出现在 [phase1-plan.md:300](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L300), [phase1-plan.md:692](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L692), [phase1-plan.md:919](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L919), [phase1-plan.md:1305](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L1305), [phase1-plan.md:1774](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L1774), [phase1-plan.md:2163](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L2163)。  
Impact: Gate 1 的测试充分性要求仍不满足，执行者在 Task 4/6/8/10/11/12 上没有可落地的入口级验证规范。  
Repair hypothesis: 给缺失任务补 5 字段契约；如果某任务仅做 stub，也要明确入口、反例和为何只能手测，否则拆出为非行为变更任务。

2. `F007`
Severity: HIGH  
Category: code-bug  
Type: defect_fix  
Before-behavior: plan 宣称 `useApi` 已全部对齐现有后端路由，但实际仍写入了错误 analytics 路径，并且把 `getPowerOptions` 注释为 Phase 2/3 待实现后，又在 Task 10 直接调用它。  
After-behavior: `useApi` 只能暴露当前真实存在的后端端点；Phase 2/3 API 不应在 Phase 1 代码中被调用。  
Evidence: plan 中 `getAnalyticsSummary/getAnalyticsDistribution/getAnalyticsQuestion/getAnalyticsGrade` 定义见 [phase1-plan.md:1369](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L1369), [phase1-plan.md:1371](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L1371), [phase1-plan.md:1373](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L1373), [phase1-plan.md:1375](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L1375)；真实路由在 [analytics/router.py:18](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/analytics/router.py#L18), [analytics/router.py:50](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/analytics/router.py#L50), [analytics/router.py:85](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/analytics/router.py#L85), [analytics/router.py:99](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/analytics/router.py#L99)。同时 `getPowerOptions` 被注释掉见 [phase1-plan.md:1427](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L1427)，但 Task 10 仍调用 `api.getPowerOptions(...)` 见 [phase1-plan.md:2268](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-haofenshu-phase1-plan.md#L2268)。  
Impact: 这不是文案问题，而是按计划实现会直接产出 404/运行时报错；Task 10 甚至无法正常运行。  
Repair hypothesis: 把 analytics 方法改成精确路由形态；`getPowerOptions` 要么从 Phase 1 删除并让 Task 10 延后，要么提供真实 stub 返回并调整调用方。

